text: You really can't beat the price, and this place makes a great pizza.  If you've never been before - you need to know that you take it home and cook it yourself.  They prepare everything and wrap it up for you to take out.  Neat concept, especially for meals a little later than when you can pick up

text: The staff here is nice and welcoming, and the pizza they make is always superb, the only thing you have to be careful of is that you know that this place doesn't bake the pizza for you, you have to take it and bake it at home, making this the freshest possible pizza you can get.
